						<div class="color-sample-block bg-white"></div>
						<div class="color-sample-text">white</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p class="mt-xxl">
				Todos estos colores, se pueden aplicar fácilmente, por ejemplo, en textos y backgrounds.
			</p>

			{% markdown %}

			```html

				<p class="text-primary-md">.text-primary-md</p>
				<p class="text-primary">.text-primary</p>
				<p class="text-secondary">.text-secondary</p>

				<p class="py-md px-sm text-white bg-success">.bg-success</p>
				<p class="py-md px-sm bg-custom-3">.bg-custom-3</p>
				<p class="py-md px-sm text-white bg-secondary-lt">.bg-secondary-lt</p>

			```
			<p class="text-primary-md">.text-primary-md</p>
			<p class="text-primary">.text-primary</p>
			<p class="text-secondary">.text-secondary</p>

			<p class="py-md px-sm text-white bg-success">.bg-success</p>
			<p class="py-md px-sm bg-custom-3">.bg-custom-3</p>
			<p class="py-md px-sm text-white bg-secondary-lt">.bg-secondary-lt</p>

			{% endmarkdown %}

		</div>
	</div>
</div>




{% endblock %}